{"tid":354945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如廁無關門被撞釀血案　支那漢刀傷兩本地男","createTime":"2017-08-11T01:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T01:57:21.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96fbb824200e0c385b1e80fba5fefab45df516b0","tid":354945,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"支那廁所無門，香港人要包容下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170811/s00001/1502413857223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170811%2Fs00001%2F1502413857223&d=vOTBSNjuBlgphOHGkzXh6ePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=0c1f1b3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170811%2Fs00001%2F1502413857223&h=6bb4d855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170811/s00001/1502413857223</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名內地漢與多名男女友人凌晨2時許光顧深水埗青山道9至15號華懋富臨門大廈地下一間食肆，前往如廁時疑未有關好廁格，一名本地男顧客前往如廁時推開廁門將他撞倒，兩人發生爭執，雙方十多人互相指駡，內地漢撿起一把利刀施襲，兩名本地客的同伴見狀出手制止，反被斬傷，本地客見狀報警。門外遺下大攤血迹，一輛停在路邊的小巴車身沾上血迹，利刀亦遺在小巴車底，警方到場拘捕內地漢。<br />\n<br />\n被捕內地漢姓孫，32歲，腳臉紅腫，孫涉嫌「傷人」罪名，正被扣留調查。據悉，孫持雙程證來港；兩名受刀傷男子均姓梁，分別28歲及30歲，主要頸部受傷，3人清醒送院。至於撞倒孫的28歲姓林本地男子受輕傷，現場接受敷治後拒絕送院，雙方男女返署協助調查，案件交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第3隊跟進。"},{"pid":"82ce0f8a219f22cc3aa506599ec024a9986b9487","tid":354945,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"睇到標題笑左出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去個廁所都要斬人<br />\n真係壓力大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5075b3f87de0d568cc180f8cab231bc8d79e1677","tid":354945,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:56:02.000Z","msg":"主要頸部受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n告意圖謀殺啦！"},{"pid":"2f1878b9e65531471d4cdcf6911be967af0e4dcf","tid":354945,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌"}]}